  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Introduction</h2>\"Can You Get Off Work on Time?\" is a domestic independent role-playing puzzle game developed by a single person.<br>In the game, you will play a worker who is about to get off work at six o'clock, but encounters a series of workplace troubles that prevent you from getting off work on time.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2>The game shows some phenomena that workers hate in the real workplace: meetings after get off work, workplace PUA, blessings, empty promises...<br>There are also those warm (unbelievable) remarks that leaders like to say. How should workers deal with these phenomena?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213770/extras/1dda21aa9f9ba82857bbfbc9ad4bc4c6.avif?t=1727515488\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213770/extras/771a7e16055c192d2699930fb2f9b412.avif?t=1727515488\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213770/extras/29a8632410ee2b36481938d0713c8822.avif?t=1727515488\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br>In the game, you need to solve the mechanisms composed of <strong>Chinese characters</strong>, <strong>radicals, splitting, moving, polyphonic characters...</strong><br><br>Experience the unique charm of Chinese culture!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213770/extras/deeb6659e67d8a173c0f4dd7ee434fd2.avif?t=1727515488\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213770/extras/4ecdc48c2198c47a65b41fdf9ca1d3e1.avif?t=1727515488\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br><strong>Finally, I hope that all the workers in the world can work from 9 to 5, and have a rest! </strong>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Introduction</h2>\"Can You Get Off Work on Time?\" is a domestic independent role-playing puzzle game developed by a single person.<br>In the game, you will play a worker who is about to get off work at six o'clock, but encounters a series of workplace troubles that prevent you from getting off work on time.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2>The game shows some phenomena that workers hate in the real workplace: meetings after get off work, workplace PUA, blessings, empty promises...<br>There are also those warm (unbelievable) remarks that leaders like to say. How should workers deal with these phenomena?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213770/extras/1dda21aa9f9ba82857bbfbc9ad4bc4c6.avif?t=1727515488\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213770/extras/771a7e16055c192d2699930fb2f9b412.avif?t=1727515488\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213770/extras/29a8632410ee2b36481938d0713c8822.avif?t=1727515488\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br>In the game, you need to solve the mechanisms composed of <strong>Chinese characters</strong>, <strong>radicals, splitting, moving, polyphonic characters...</strong><br><br>Experience the unique charm of Chinese culture!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213770/extras/deeb6659e67d8a173c0f4dd7ee434fd2.avif?t=1727515488\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213770/extras/4ecdc48c2198c47a65b41fdf9ca1d3e1.avif?t=1727515488\